HSBC Global Asset Management (Taiwan) Limited: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 10:19 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of HSBC Global Asset Management (Taiwan) Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
HSBC Global Asset Management (Taiwan) Limited provides its services primarily to investment companies. It also serves Corporations and municipal government entities. The firm manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual fund for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. HSBC Global Asset Management (Taiwan) Limited is based in Taipei, Taiwan. HSBC Global Asset Management (Taiwan) Limited operates as a subsidiary of HSBC Global Asset Management (UK) Limited.


24th Floor99 Tun haw South RoadSection 2Taipei,  106Taiwan



Phone: 886 2 2325 7888

Fax: 886 2 2325 9086

www.assetmanagement.hsbc.com.tw







